quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  42,32,"Hino jeyaa e maandeeji Makko ɗin: dogayɗe ɗen ka maayo, wa'uɗe wa pelle"
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O deeƴinay henndu ndun, ndu waɗtinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e ɗum, maandeeji, wonannde kala muññotooɗo, yettoowo"
  42,34,Maa yooliraɗe sabu ko ɓe faggitii kon. Himo yaafoo non ko ɗuuɗi
  42,35,"Wennjooɓe ɓen e Aayeeje Amen ɗen, hino anndi ɓe alaa laaworde"
  42,36,"Kala ko okkaɗon e huunde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah kon, ɓuri moƴƴude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonannde gomɗimɓe ɓen fawotooɓe e Joomi maɓɓe"
  42,37,"woɗɗitotooɓe bakkaatuuji mawɗi ɗin e pankare ɗen, si wonii ɓe tikkii, hara ɓe yaafoto"
  42,38,"ɓen nootiiɓe Joomi maɓɓe, ɓe ñiɓni julde nden, ɓe tawata fiyaaku maɓɓe on ko diisondiral hakkunde maɓɓe, nafqooɓe e kon ko Men arsiki ɓe"
  42,39,"e ɓen tawɓe si bewre heɓii ɓe, ɓe yottoto"
  42,40,"Njoɓdi bonnere, ko bone yeru mun. Kala non yaafiiɗo o moƴƴintini, haray njoɓdi makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yiɗaa tooñooɓe ɓen"
  42,41,"Kala non yottiiɓe ɓaawo ɓe tooñeede, ko ɓen woni ɓe laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mun"
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mun, ko tooñooɓe yimɓe ɓen, hara hiɓe bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: ɓe ɗon, hino woodani lepte muusuɗe"
  42,43,"Muññiiɗo on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, ɗum no jeyaa e pellital fiyakuujI"
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray giɗo (goo) alanaa mo ɓaawo ɗum. A tinay tooñuɓe ɓen, tuma ɓe yi'i lepte ɗen, hiɓe wi'a: \"Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi"